data.meta_description: Title April 2018 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document appears to be a list of songs from April 2018 arranged by title. It includes over 100 songs listed as duets or featuring other artists. The songs span various genres and decades. Many are collaborations between popular artists like Shania Twain, Dolly Parton, Mariah Carey, and Elvis Presley.
